        <Parent_String>gilding (technique) [300053789], metallizing [300053985], surface covering processes and techniques [300229469], additive and joining processes and techniques [300229467], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
